These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, manager, engineer, nurse
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, baking, photography, filmmaking
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, yellow, lavender, white
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, epic, animation, horror
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the project-manager is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the nurse##1
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 6. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the manager##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is the engineer##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
10. the project-manager is the person watching horror movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job          | engineer  | project-manager    | nurse    | manager   |
| Hobby   | baking     | gardening   | photography       | filmmaking    |
| Color   | yellow | fuchsia | white    | lavender |
| Movie-Genre           | epic | horror       | sports | animation     |

