.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, police-officer, photographer, doctor
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, musical, disaster
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, chess, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, mirinda, lemonade, soy-milk
 1. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
 2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the photographer##1
 4. the police-officer is the person playing whist##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the teacher##1
 6. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
 7. the doctor is on the right of the photographer##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 9. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
10. the photographer is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing chess is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Job          | teacher  | police-officer    | photographer     | doctor       |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | disaster | documentary   | horror |
| Game   | chess | whist   | scrabble   | poker    |
| Beverage         | lemonade | soy-milk  | sprite | mirinda   |

