.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, rock, country, d&b
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, lily, tulip, aconite
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, game, alhambra
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, mah-jongg, domino
 1. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
 2. the blend-smoker is the person who growstulip##1
 3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 5. the fan of rock is the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person playing whist is the alhambra-smoker##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
 9. the fan of country is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
10. the person playing whist is the fan of country##1
11. the fan of reggae is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | reggae | country   | d&b    | rock      |
| Flower           | tulip | rose | lily | aconite     |
| Cigar   | blend      | alhambra   | montecristo   | game |
| Game           | domino         | whist       | mah-jongg  | backgammon       |

