.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, lawyer, scientist, dressmaker
City: paris, london, miami, edinburgh
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, blend, old-henry, havana
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, turtle, goldfish
 1. the designer is the person traveling to paris##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 4. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the lawyer is the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the designer##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
 9. the owner of the turtle is the blend-smoker##1
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
11. the scientist is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Job   | dressmaker       | scientist   | designer   | lawyer   |
| City       | london        | edinburgh | paris    | miami       |
| Cigar      | havana | blend    | old-henry  | swisher |
| Pet      | ferret  | turtle  | chinchilla | goldfish    |

