.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, crime, satire
House: ranch-style, art-deco, futuristic, gothic-revival
City: miami, san-francisco, prague, marseilles
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, pony, rabbit
 1. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the futuristic house is between the owner of the fish and the person watching satire movies##2
 3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 6. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person traveling to miami##1
 8. the futuristic house is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
10. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
12. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Movie-Genre    | crime    | satire      | animation          | mystery    |
| House   | art-deco | gothic-revival       | futuristic | ranch-style |
| City     | marseilles     | prague      | san-francisco     | miami |
| Pet   | snake   | rabbit | pony        | fish   |

