.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
House: palace, ranch-style, cape-cod, craftsman
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, photographer, journalist, teacher
4 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, bridge, chess
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, january, march
 1. the journalist is on the left of the palace house##1
 2. the palace house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 3. the entrepreneur is on the right of the photographer##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 5. the palace house is in an odd position##4
 6. the person playing chess is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person playing monopoly##2
 7. the person playing bridge is the journalist##1
 8. the ranch-style house is the journalist##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| House      | cape-cod  | ranch-style    | palace       | craftsman       |
| Job          | teacher    | journalist | photographer | entrepreneur     |
| Game   | billiard | bridge        | chess    | monopoly   |
| Birthday   | october  | january      | march    | june |

