.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, may, december
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, tulip, bellflower, daisy
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, tea, 7up
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, light-blue, mauve
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 8. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
10. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
12. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | october | may    | december  | january      |
| Flower   | iris      | bellflower | daisy | tulip   |
| Beverage           | tea       | 7up | fanta   | almond-milk       |
| Color     | mauve      | light-blue | ivory  | brown |

