.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, february, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bike, tram, van
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, engineer, software-developer, chef
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, chestnut, blood-red, yellow
 1. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes blood-red##2
 3. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
 5. the chef is on the right of the software-developer##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 7. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the engineer##1
 9. the person who likes mauve is between the fisherman and the person driving the bike##2
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday         | april  | february    | march    | july |
| Transport   | tram   | train       | bike  | van    |
| Job   | fisherman | engineer | software-developer | chef   |
| Color           | blood-red    | mauve        | yellow   | chestnut    |

