 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the security-guard##1
 5. the security-guard is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 6. the lawyer is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the german is in an odd position##4
 8. the havana-smoker is the lawyer##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
10. the security-guard is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
12. the australian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
13. the pakistani is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
