 8. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
11. the townhouse house is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
