 9. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

