 8. the italian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 9. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in march is the bluemaster-smoker##1
11. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
12. the colombian is on the left or right of the italian##3
13. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

