There 4 different types of food: lime, apricot, cabbage, broccoli
 1. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 2. the person eating broccoli is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
 4. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the fan of trance##1
