 9. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
10. the victorian house is between the pall-mall-smoker and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
11. the owner of the frog is on the right of the victorian house##1
12. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3

.:: Answer ::.
