|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| House      | townhouse   | wooden   | victorian     | gothic-revival   |
| Hobby   | drawing  | photography       | skydiving | rock-climbing |
| Flower           | sunflower     | daffodil   | daisy     | iris     |
| Game         | billiard | go | poker   | backgammon |

