.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, dutch, american, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, bike, jet-ski, train
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, february, may
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, orchid, azalea
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the nigerian##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the japanese##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
12. the person driving the bus is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality      | american       | dutch | japanese        | nigerian        |
| Transport         | train | jet-ski       | bus | bike |
| Birthday   | may     | october        | december    | february      |
| Flower         | daffodil     | orchid    | azalea | poppy   |

