.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, thriller, sports
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, october, april
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, bartender, paramedic, analyst
4 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, hedgehog, dog
 1. the person watching sports movies is the paramedic##1
 2. the paramedic is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 3. the paramedic is on the left or right of the photographer##3
 4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the photographer is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is the bartender##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
 9. the bartender is on the left or right of the photographer##3
10. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
12. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | animation | sports     | thriller        |
| Birthday   | october | april  | september     | november |
| Job         | bartender    | photographer | paramedic      | analyst |
| Pet     | dog | chinchilla     | hedgehog | lizard       |

 